file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: OpenAPI MQ Sender
  license:
    name: MIT
servers:
  - url: 'http://nqsender.lightapi.net'
paths:
  /put:
    post:
      summary: Put a key/value pair to a queue for receiver to get
      operationId: put
      requestBody:
        description: A key/value pair
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ValueObject'
      tags:
        - put
      security:
        - mq_auth:
            - 'mq.w'
            - 'mq.r'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Null response
  /pub:
    post:
      summary: Publish a key/value pair to a topic for subscribers
      operationId: pub
      requestBody:
        description: A key/value pair
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/ValueObject'
      tags:
        - pub
      security:
        - mq_auth:
            - 'mq.w'
            - 'mq.r'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: Null response
components:
  securitySchemes:
    mq_auth:
      type: oauth2
      description: This API uses OAuth 2.0 with the client credential grant flow.
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          tokenUrl: 'https://localhost:6882/token'
          scopes:
            'mq.w': write MQ sender
            'mq.r': read MQ sender
  schemas:
    ValueObject:
      type: object
      required:
        - key
        - value
      properties:
        key:
          type: string
        value:
          type: string
